          "text": "Sure, I’m ready to go through it.",
          "timestamp": "2026-02-01T20:26:56.577Z"
        },
        {
          "role": "agent",
          "text": "All right, the total outstanding balance is $2,450, and it’s 45 days past due. We can look at either a one-time payment or set up a payment plan. What kind of payment arrangement would work best for you right now?",
          "timestamp": "2026-02-01T20:27:01.502Z"
        },
        {
          "role": "user",
          "text": "Hmm, I think a payment plan would be best for me right now. That way I can manage it more comfortably.",
          "timestamp": "2026-02-01T20:27:05.824Z"
        },
        {
          "role": "agent",
          "text": "That makes sense, John. We can set up a monthly payment plan. Let’s find an amount that fits your budget—what monthly payment are you comfortable with?",
          "timestamp": "2026-02-01T20:27:08.777Z"
        },
        {
          "role": "user",
          "text": "Well, I think I could manage around $200 a month.",
          "timestamp": "2026-02-01T20:27:12.147Z"
        },
        {
          "role": "agent",
          "text": "Understood, John. At $200 a month, it would take about 12 months to clear the balance. Let me confirm if that arrangement works and we’ll finalize the details.",
